     <period-start iso-date="2019-01-01"></period-start>
     <period-end iso-date="2019-12-31"></period-end>
     <target>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.1. (1) Development of An MoU between the Supreme Court and the Judicial Commission on Joint Examination Procedures
1.1. (2) Development of SOP on the Judicial Ethic Council
1.1. (3) Integration of the Supreme Court&#x2019;s complaint handling mechanism in SIWAS application with the Judicial Commission&#x2019;s application

1.2. (1) Launch and TOT of e-monev application
1.2. (2) Technical Assistance of e-monev application
1.2. (3) Assistance in testing the survey module and assessment for survey for public satisfactory on court services
1.2. (4) Trainings for BAWAS personnel on Audit skills (with BPKP)</narrative>
      </comment>
     </target>
     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.1. SUSTAIN project was not able to complete any objective due to inactivity at the Judicial Commission and Supreme Court.

1.2. (1) The application was further developed and its accompanying regulation was drafted. however, up until the project ended, BAWAS still hasnt formalize the applicaton. Therefore, TOT and launch was unable to be completed.
1.2. (2) Since the e-Monev is unable to be formalized in time by the project ended, the technical assistance was not able to be implemented
1.2. (3) The survey was tested in several cities and was launched to the public at 27 May 2019.
1.2. (4) This activity was unable to be implemented due to limited time the project has.</narrative>
      </comment>
     </actual>
